Trying out some Java 7 stuff. 
- Try with resources
- Fork/Join
- FileWalker
- WatchService
- Multi-catch
- Diamond operator
- Switch on String


The WordCount class counts occurences of the given search phrase in all Java files under the specified directory. It calculates the speed inprovement by first running single-threaded and then running in a fork/join pool.


The Fork/Join code was copied from this article:
http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/articles/java/fork-join-422606.html

